Local Char    CODMSKDEF(GLONAMK) , CMEMO(GLONAMM)
Local Libelle MAGNETO
Local Char    ZSITE(GLONAVA), ZACC(GLONAVA)
Call TEXTE(44887,TITT) From OBJDIV
TIT        = mess(15,126,1)
If dim(CNSCOD)>0 : TIT -= CNSCOD : Endif
PROGSTD    = "CNSPPDSTD"
PROGSPE    = "CNSPPDSPE"
CBOITE     = "DCRITPPD"
BOITE      = "FCNSPPD"
NOMMSK(0)  = "CONSPPD1"
ABMSK(0)   = "PPD1"
NOMMSK(1)  = "CONSPPD2"
ABMSK(1)   = "PPD2"
CMEMO      = "ppd"
CNOMMSK    = "CRITPPD"
CABMSK     = "CPPD"
MAGNETO    = 1
Return

$SETCLE
Local Char    CLE(10), CLECMP(10)(0..0), CLEMSK(10)(0..0)
